<lb n="9"/>kaṇakku vi<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>nā<hi rend="grantha">tha</hi> ṉum kaṇakkiṉpaṭi teṉṉārināṭṭu teṉkāciyil <unclear>ko</unclear>yil tāṉattāril Oñcāṇṭikkāttāṉ vakaiyāka na<unclear>m</unclear>
<lb n="10"/>kaṇṭuḻavu tirntu Ivv<unclear>āṇṭu</unclear> pacāṉa mutalukku kārpacānam payircceytukoḷḷumpaṭi kaṟpittu viṭṭa mutaṟkaṇṇāṟu taṭi Oṉṟu nila
<lb n="11" break="no"/>m Araikkāṇi muntirikaiyiṉ mākāṇiyum Iraṇṭāṅ kaṇṇāṟu taṭi Iraṇṭu nilam Araikkāṇi muntirikaiyum taṭi Iraṇṭu nilam kāṇi
